Source: pg-eviltransform
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~), libgeos-dev, librttopo-dev, pkg-config, cargo, clang
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/aiyou178/pg_eviltransform

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-eviltransform
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-eviltransform
Depends: postgresql-PGVERSION, postgresql-PGVERSION-postgis-3, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Coordinate transform extension based on eviltransform
  Rust/pgrx extension providing bd09 and gcj02 coordinate transform helpers
  for PostgreSQL/PostGIS workflows.
